title: ETHIOPIAN CABBAGE AND POTATOES
directions: Heat the olive oil in large skillet over medium heat. Cook the carrots and onions in the hot oil for about 5 minutes. Stir in salt, pepper, cumin, turmeric and cabbage and cook about another 15 minutes. Add potatoes, cover and reduce heat to medium low and cook for about 25 - 30 minutes, stirring occasionally,
until potatoes are soft. (Mine took 30 minutes.)
ingredients: 5 potatoes, peeled and cup up into 1 inch cubes
